            "title": "水温对使用时机的影响",
            "content": "水温是决定何时使用抽停米诺的关键因素之一：\n1. **低温环境**：当水温低于15.5度时，使用抽停米诺的机会超过50%[[87](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1743699401&ver=5908&signature=ssQQFmAg65r4u0kuAmhQORr*W-8oda7MtA*YWTPOGpvO-t4z5Te79PXmcbvcEr6OCuDyScGx4G*hoA25NUv2eH8pvJeydpnfQTioJ5fLdDE13JAyVxACs4ElQSw4buhq&new=1)]。水温越低，抽后停止时间可以增长[[76](https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/672d7900000000003c0149f6?xsec_token=ABZm1KTImWDlu9Oru8rBhi7_SLePGa7twzyyfHs7hrziQ=&xsec_source=)]。\n2. **高温环境**：在夏季或水温较高的情况下，抽停米诺的效果可能不佳，尤其是对大嘴鲈鱼而言[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。",
