            "title": "型号选择",
            "content": "抽停米诺的型号选择主要考虑以下几个方面：\n1. **水性选择**：\n   - **悬停型**：适合在鱼可能在较深水层的情况使用，尤其是在冬季[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n   - **浮水型**：适合在鱼靠近水面或在浅水区活动时使用，特别是在产卵阶段[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n2. **身体外形选择**：\n   - **窄身体**：适合在水温较低时使用，动作幅度较小[[9](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1a64y1W71b/)]。\n   - **圆鼓身体**：适合在水温较高时使用，动作幅度较大[[9](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1a64y1W71b/)]。\n3. **尺寸选择**：\n   - 一般抽停米诺的尺寸在80~120毫米之间[[1](https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/142664947)]。\n   - 在北方，有时使用3英寸以下的饵，当小嘴在追逐小饵鱼时[[87](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1743699401&ver=5908&signature=ssQQFmAg65r4u0kuAmhQORr*W-8oda7MtA*YWTPOGpvO-t4z5Te79PXmcbvcEr6OCuDyScGx4G*hoA25NUv2eH8pvJeydpnfQTioJ5fLdDE13JAyVxACs4ElQSw4buhq&new=1)]。\n   - 尺寸选择主要考虑饵鱼的大小，如果饵鱼比较大，可以选择更大的尺寸[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n4. **颜色选择**：\n   - **清澈水质**：透明、鲜黄色或不透明、鲜艳色[[76](https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/672d7900000000003c0149f6?xsec_token=ABZm1KTImWDlu9Oru8rBhi7_SLePGa7twzyyfHs7hrziQ=&xsec_source=)]。\n   - **半透明水质**：半透明、鲜艳色[[76](https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/672d7900000000003c0149f6?xsec_token=ABZm1KTImWDlu9Oru8rBhi7_SLePGa7twzyyfHs7hrziQ=&xsec_source=)]。\n   - **不透明水质**：不透明、鲜艳色[[76](https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/672d7900000000003c0149f6?xsec_token=ABZm1KTImWDlu9Oru8rBhi7_SLePGa7twzyyfHs7hrziQ=&xsec_source=)]。\n   - **饵鱼类型**：在南部地区，选择shad颜色，带有蓝色或黑色头部和一点点亮绿色；在北部地区，选择perch颜色，如Firetiger色[[87](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1743699401&ver=5908&signature=ssQQFmAg65r4u0kuAmhQORr*W-8oda7MtA*YWTPOGpvO-t4z5Te79PXmcbvcEr6OCuDyScGx4G*hoA25NUv2eH8pvJeydpnfQTioJ5fLdDE13JAyVxACs4ElQSw4buhq&new=1)]。\n   - **鱼种**：对于小嘴鲈或斑点鲈，鲜艳的颜色有时对鱼更有吸引力，可以尝试亮绿或橙黄色的鱼饵[[87](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1743699401&ver=5908&signature=ssQQFmAg65r4u0kuAmhQORr*W-8oda7MtA*YWTPOGpvO-t4z5Te79PXmcbvcEr6OCuDyScGx4G*hoA25NUv2eH8pvJeydpnfQTioJ5fLdDE13JAyVxACs4ElQSw4buhq&new=1)]。\n   - **肚子颜色**：鱼主要看到的是饵的肚子，然后是一小部分侧面的颜色。有些人使用亮绿色或者黄色肚子的米诺效果很好。有些鱼因为长期贴近水底，肚子可能会呈现出橘色的颜色，这就是黄色肚子能钓到鱼的原因[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。",
