            "title": "不同季节的操作技巧",
            "content": "1. **春季**：\n   - 早晨鱼口期时，抽停频率可以快一些，中午光照强湿度高可以慢一点[[76](https://www.xiaohongshu.com/search_result/672d7900000000003c0149f6?xsec_token=ABZm1KTImWDlu9Oru8rBhi7_SLePGa7twzyyfHs7hrziQ=&xsec_source=)]。\n   - 针对产前的鲈鱼，寻找崖壁的台阶、45度角的河岸、延伸到主湖区的尖脊或桥墩等位置[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n2. **夏季**：\n   - 在清澈的湖面上，每次抽的距离短一些，让饵尽量长时间地留在攻击区域内[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n   - 在夏季，如果发现鱼集群，就使用jerkbait[[87](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?src=11&timestamp=1743699401&ver=5908&signature=ssQQFmAg65r4u0kuAmhQORr*W-8oda7MtA*YWTPOGpvO-t4z5Te79PXmcbvcEr6OCuDyScGx4G*hoA25NUv2eH8pvJeydpnfQTioJ5fLdDE13JAyVxACs4ElQSw4buhq&new=1)]。\n3. **秋季**：\n   - 初秋时，和夏天有点像，可以在湾子里钓到鱼，所以浮水的米诺效果会更好[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n   - 随着水温降低，鱼开始往外退，寻找尖脊或深浅变化的位置[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n4. **冬季**：\n   - 冬季作钓，一定是使用悬停米诺，需要去寻找陡峭的崖壁，因为这里接近深水[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。\n   - 有暖流流入的区域，以及水温相对更高的支流和湾子里，也是可以去尝试的[[8](https://weixin.sogou.com/link?url=dn9a_-gY295K0Rci_xozVXfdMkSQTLW6cwJThYulHEtVjXrGTiVgS816RxrAx1MIznpP0ER6BSQg_ZRT-GH9E1qXa8Fplpd9sUaiXmwiVB0iZi7i3Z5Pivw5aBKE_Pv9YGk4YZ9LJ-hZue9RgCm0r63w3Wdovc3y1Qd7xSDEH1lRtONHKblTg_f_MZNypO0LXImwW6EzS7HUYxont8BIicrqbPj5NY-QxF7RWTZlqAkLDSfYX7UwEeqOuooxXYcdOR2w0jACLoaFW6cwuUnkdA..&type=2&query=%E6%8A%�%20%E6%8A%BD%E5%81%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%AF%BA%20Jerkbait%20%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%9A%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7&token=11D1BFAA410DE7E09A9CAA515FBAED9B9B97B23C67EEBDC9)]。",
